movie.title: Planet of the Apes
movie.plot: An  U.S. Spaceship lands on a desolate planet, stranding astronaut Taylor in a world dominated by apes, 2000 years into the future, who use a primitive race of humans for experimentation and sport. Soon Taylor finds himself among the hunted, his life in the hands of a benevolent chimpanzee scientist.
movie.awards: Nominated for 2 Oscars. Another 6 wins & 2 nominations.
